Articles.Content:
hi all. so the game seems to work well except when i "revert to launch" i get a nice view of space as if the planetary system has disappeared. these are my current mods... 000_Toolbar, EVE, RcsSounds, Scatterer, StageRecovery, SVE and Wheelsounds have not officially been updated to 113.

 

and this is a copy and paste of my log, it might as well be chinese to me, so i copied as much as i think would help. let me know if you need moar.
